<DocsLayout title="buoy anchor" description="Anchor your design system with AI-powered token generation">
  <h1>buoy anchor</h1>

  <p>
    Anchor your design system by analyzing your codebase and establishing design tokens.
    Uses AI to understand patterns and generate a coherent token system.
  </p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>

  <pre><code>buoy anchor [options]</code></pre>

  <h2>Options</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Option</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--fresh</code></td>
        <td>Generate a fresh design system instead of extracting from code</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--style &lt;style&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Style preset: minimal, bold, soft, corporate</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--primary-color &lt;color&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Primary brand color (hex)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--framework &lt;framework&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Target framework: react, vue, svelte, vanilla</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--output &lt;path&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Output directory or file path (default: ".")</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--extend &lt;file&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Extend existing token file</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--no-ai</code></td>
        <td>Skip AI analysis (use heuristics only)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--pr</code></td>
        <td>Create a GitHub PR with the generated tokens</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--json</code></td>
        <td>Output as JSON</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Examples</h2>

  <h3>Extract tokens from existing code</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy anchor

Analyzing codebase...

Found 47 unique colors
Found 12 unique spacing values
Found 8 unique font sizes

Generated tokens.css with 67 tokens
Generated tokens.json</code></pre>

  <h3>Generate fresh design system</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy anchor --fresh --style minimal --primary-color "#3b82f6"

Generating minimal design system...

Created:
  - tokens.css (42 tokens)
  - tokens.json
  - tailwind.tokens.js</code></pre>

  <h3>Create PR with tokens</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy anchor --pr

Analyzing codebase...
Creating PR...

PR created: https://github.com/org/repo/pull/123</code></pre>

  <h2>Style Presets</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>minimal</strong> - Clean, subtle design with neutral tones</li>
    <li><strong>bold</strong> - High contrast with vibrant colors</li>
    <li><strong>soft</strong> - Rounded, gentle aesthetic</li>
    <li><strong>corporate</strong> - Professional, enterprise-ready</li>
  </ul>

